<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wisata Pagar Alam - Surga di Sumsel</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS INTERNAL */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        :root {
            --hijau: #228B22;
            --kuning: #FFD700;
            --merah: #FF0000;
            --putih: #ffffff;
            --hitam: #333;
        }

        body { line-height: 1.6; color: var(--hitam); }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            background-color: var(--hijau);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--kuning);
        }

        .logo { color: var(--putih); font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .logo span { color: var(--kuning); }

        nav ul { display: flex; list-style: none; }
        nav ul li { margin-left: 20px; }
        nav ul li a { 
            color: var(--putih); 
            text-decoration: none; 
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        nav ul li a:hover { color: var(--kuning); }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 80vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1572455825634-2c64fc79555c?q=80&w=2000') no-repeat center center/cover;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: var(--putih);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 10px; text-shadow: 2px 2px var(--merah); }
        
        .search-bar {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .search-bar input {
            border: none;
            padding: 10px;
            flex: 1;
            outline: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .btn-search {
            background: var(--merah);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Highlights */
        .container { padding: 50px 5%; }
        .section-title { 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-bottom: 40px; 
            color: var(--hijau);
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--kuning);
            display: inline-block;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            position: relative;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .card img { width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; }
        .card-content { padding: 20px; }
        .card-content h3 { color: var(--hijau); margin-bottom: 10px; }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav { flex-direction: column; }
            nav ul { margin-top: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
            nav ul li { margin: 5px 10px; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">PAGAR<span>ALAM</span></div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="destinasi.html">Destinasi</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Aktivitas</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Budaya</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Kuliner</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Trip Plan</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Booking</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Jelajahi Keindahan Gunung Dempo</h1>
        <p>Temukan kedamaian di hamparan kebun teh dan air terjun yang megah.</p>
        <div class="search-bar">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Cari: Pantai, Kuliner, Budaya...">
            <button class="btn-search">Cari</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="container">
        <center><h2 class="section-title">Highlight Destinasi</h2></center>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x250" alt="Gunung Dempo">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Gunung Dempo</h3>
                    <p>Ikon wisata Pagar Alam dengan hamparan kebun teh yang hijau dan udara yang sejuk.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x250" alt="Air Terjun Maung">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Air Terjun Maung</h3>
                    <p>Air terjun unik dengan aliran air yang melebar melalui dinding hijau.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x250" alt="Situs Megalithikum">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Situs Megalithikum</h3>
                    <p>Warisan sejarah zaman batu yang tersebar di wilayah Tegur Wangi.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer style="background: var(--hitam); color: white; text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Pagar Alam Tourism - Aneu Rianti X PPLG 1</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>

